description:
Merchants that provide services to medical and dental professionals
and to patients referred by physicians or dentists. Includes medical
laboratories that perform biological analysis, blood analysis,
urinalysis, X-ray, bacteriological analysis, and diagnostic analysis, and
dental laboratories that make dentures, artificial teeth, crowns and
bridges, and customized orthodontic appliances.
